readable.content: A girl messily eats a plate of pasta . A little girl in a high chair is messily eating spaghetti . A little girl makes a mess on her hand and face while eating in her baby chair . A young girl sits in a high chair and eats red food while making a mess . The girl eating spaghetti is wearing a red jacket .
